description:
&lt;p&gt;Do you want to be a part of our friendly, dynamic and amazing team?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a highly motivated, hard-working and enthusiastic Staff Nurse to join our team in Ward 2 Gastroenterology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ward 2 Gastroenterology is a 24 bedded medical ward caring for a variety of male and female patients with acute medical conditions specialising in gastroenterology and general medicine. The post will provide the opportunity to enhance their knowledge and skills related to this specialty. Our team aim to provide high quality service in a safe environment for all our patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We will offer you opportunities for you to enhance your clinical skills within gastroenterology and acute medicine. We will provide support and encouragement to enable you to develop and achieve your full potential. The ward offers the suitable candidate the opportunity to work within our respected multidisciplinary team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This an exciting opportunity for nurses and if you are interested in this post we would like to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dana Victorino - Senior Sister&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: dana.victorino@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 01753 633962&lt;/p&gt;
